text: Lego Scooby-Doo! Haunted Hollywood is a Lego movie about 4 teenagers: Fred, Daphne, Velma, and Shaggy, and a dog named Scooby-Doo. They're here to make movies. == Main cast == * Frank Welker as Scooby-Doo, and Fred * Matthew Lillard as Shaggy * Grey DeLisle as Daphne * Kate Micucci as Velma Category:2016 movies Category:Lego movies Category:Warner Bros. direct-to- video movies
